### ==============================================
### POSTS (CRUD)
### ==============================================

### Criar Post (sem arquivos)
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{estudanteToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MyBoundary

--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="texto"

Meu post com links
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="links"

["https://google.com", "https://youtube.com"]
--MyBoundary--


### Criar Post (com upload de arquivos)
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{estudanteToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MyBoundary

--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="texto"

Meus post com upload de arquivos!
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="links"

["https://exemplo.com/resource"]
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="arquivos"; filename="imagem1.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./uploads_test/imagem1.png
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="arquivos"; filename="doc1.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./uploads_test/doc1.pdf
--MyBoundary--


### Editar Post
PUT  {{baseUrl}}/posts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{estudanteToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MyBoundary

--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="texto"

Texto atualizado do post!
--MyBoundary--

